graph LR
    ODHModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>v1.27.0-rhods-427]

    %% External Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|serves models| KServe[KServe v0.12.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelController -->|serverless autoscaling| Knative[Knative Serving v0.39.3<br/>OPTIONAL - Serverless mode only]
    ODHModelController -->|traffic mgmt & mTLS| Istio[Istio/Maistra Service Mesh 1.19.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -->|API authorization| Authorino[Authorino v0.15.0<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -->|external routing| OpenShiftRoute[OpenShift Route API 3.9.0+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelController -->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager or OpenShift Service CA<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|watches & updates| KServeCRDs[KServe CRDs<br/>InferenceService, ServingRuntime]
    ODHModelController -->|model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelController -->|reads config| DSC[DataScienceCluster<br/>datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io]
    ODHModelController -->|reads platform config| DSCI[DSCInitialization<br/>dscinitialization.opendatahub.io]
    ODHModelController -.->|integrates with| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>sidecars, mTLS]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| ODHModelController
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| ODHModelController

    %% External Services
    ODHModelController -->|watches resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
    KServe -->|loads models from| S3[S3 Object Storage<br/>AWS S3, MinIO, etc.]

    %% Deployed Resources (Created by Controller)
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| IstioResources[Istio Resources<br/>VirtualService, Gateway,<br/>PeerAuthentication]
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| AuthConfigs[AuthConfig<br/>authorino.kuadrant.io]
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>route.openshift.io]
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicy<br/>networking.k8s.io]
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| Monitoring[ServiceMonitor, PodMonitor<br/>monitoring.coreos.com]

    %% Serving Runtime Templates
    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| OVMS[OVMS Runtime<br/>OpenVINO Model Server]
    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| TGIS[TGIS Runtime<br/>Text Generation]
    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| Caikit[Caikit Runtime<br/>Caikit-TGIS, Standalone]
    ODHModelController -.->|deploys templates| vLLM[vLLM Runtime<br/>High-throughput LLM]

